# Example environment file for `mind`.
#
# Copy to `~/.mind/.env` (global) and/or `<your-project>/.env` (per-repo).
# Control precedence with `api_key_source` in `~/.mind/config.yml`:
#   env_first      — shell exports win over `.env` files
#   dotenv_first   — `.env` files win over shell exports
#
# Never commit real secrets.

# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-or-...
